00:53:26,450 --> 00:53:27,251
Can I finish the neg' ?

1002
00:53:29,840 --> 00:53:30,880
Here yo go.
It's much better like that.

1003
00:53:30,890 --> 00:53:31,720
So, how much was it?

1004
00:53:31,721 --> 00:53:32,589
It's on me...

1005
00:53:32,590 --> 00:53:33,952
Thank you.

1006
00:53:38,630 --> 00:53:40,130
Is... is that clear?

1007
00:53:42,650 --> 00:53:44,850
Hell!
Your masculine side is quite in-your-face.

1008
00:53:44,851 --> 00:53:45,851
Why did you act like that, Andre?

1009
00:53:45,852 --> 00:53:46,852
What did I do wrong?

1010
00:53:47,660 --> 00:53:48,660
What is this?

1011
00:53:49,710 --> 00:53:50,710
Where did you get it?

1012
00:53:50,711 --> 00:53:51,711
Why didn't you give him his 10 Euros?

1013
00:53:51,712 --> 00:53:52,712
Why did you care?

1014
00:53:53,800 --> 00:53:55,110
Can't we talk about that a bit further?
Come...

1015
00:53:55,111 --> 00:53:57,450
Those 10 Euros weren't even yours.
I gave them.

1016
00:53:57,451 --> 00:53:59,350
Exactly : that's all we have left.
Let's go!

1017
00:53:59,351 --> 00:54:03,250
You spend your time finding ways not to communicate, Andre.
You're all over the place. Up to no good.

1018
00:54:03,251 --> 00:54:04,251
Sorry for interrupting...

1019
00:54:04,252 --> 00:54:05,050
You! Shut up! Okay?

1020
00:54:05,051 --> 00:54:08,050
