What do you see?

1127
00:58:48,000 --> 00:58:49,000
I don't know.

1128
00:58:49,001 --> 00:58:50,300
Good.
You're improving.

1129
00:58:50,301 --> 00:58:51,000
You think so?

1130
00:58:51,001 --> 00:58:52,850
Yes.
All you used to see was a pile of crap.

1131
00:58:52,851 --> 00:58:54,500
Now, you don't see anything anymore.

1132
00:58:54,501 --> 00:58:56,500
It means you've cleaned up the place.

1133
00:58:56,501 --> 00:59:00,230
Now, we need to
fill that empty shell with something.

1134
00:59:00,920 --> 00:59:02,420
You can't leave it like that.

1135
00:59:02,710 --> 00:59:05,120
So, take a good look.
In front of you...

1136
00:59:05,121 --> 00:59:09,450
Isn't there anything you like,
in this beautiful face?

1137
00:59:14,350 --> 00:59:15,450
Not much, no...

1138
00:59:15,451 --> 00:59:19,510
Look carefully. In your eyes.
What do you see?

1139
00:59:25,300 --> 00:59:27,265
Some... some kindness?

1140
00:59:27,266 --> 00:59:30,885
Yes there is. A lot...
What else?

1141
00:59:37,760 --> 00:59:39,230
They're not too bad?

1142
00:59:39,231 --> 00:59:41,600
Beauty. That's right.

1143
00:59:41,601 --> 00:59:42,945
They are beautiful.

1144
00:59:43,340 --> 00:59:44,340
What else?

1145
00:59:49,750 --> 00:59:51,000
Maybe...

1146
00:59:52,666 --> 00:59:53,800
Some sweetness?

1147
00:59:53,801 --> 00:59:56,560
Yes.
Lots of it.

1148
00:59:56,950 --> 00:59:58,650
And love?

1149
00:59:58,651 --> 00:59:59,651
Yeah.

1150
01:00:01,320 --> 01:00:03,190
Lots of love, yes.

1151
01:00:04,110 --> 01:00:05,350
Too much, maybe.

1152
01:00:05,351 --> 01:00:07,250
If there's too much,
you need to get it out.

1153
01:00:08,000 --> 01:00:09,000
Tell me you love me.

1154
01:00:09,001 --> 01:00:09,950
