1155
01:00:09,965 --> 01:00:10,795
Don't you love me?

1156
01:00:10,800 --> 01:00:12,003
I do.
A lot.

1157
01:00:12,004 --> 01:00:13,004
I mean...

1158
01:00:13,800 --> 01:00:15,550
