1159
01:00:15,551 --> 01:00:16,875
But maybe it's friendship, and...

1160
01:00:16,876 --> 01:00:19,590
Do you love me, or not?

1161
01:00:24,215 --> 01:00:25,815
Since the first day.

1162
01:00:27,990 --> 01:00:29,490
Since the first second.

1163
01:00:29,491 --> 01:00:31,645
Good.
Say it, then.

1164
01:00:38,350 --> 01:00:40,700
It's...
It's hard to say.

1165
01:00:40,701 --> 01:00:41,701
Do you know why?

1166
01:00:42,040 --> 01:00:42,702
No.

1167
01:00:42,703 --> 01:00:44,500
Because nobody ever told it to you.

1168
01:00:44,650 --> 01:00:45,900
Right?

1169
01:00:47,500 --> 01:00:51,350
It's difficult to love yourself,
when nobody shows you how.

1170
01:00:52,275 --> 01:00:53,275
Yes.

1171
01:00:55,440 --> 01:00:57,440
I love you, Andre.

1172
01:00:58,280 --> 01:01:00,615
Here you go.
You have received love.

1173
01:01:00,616 --> 01:01:02,615
Now you can give some away.

1174
01:01:02,616 --> 01:01:03,840
Go for it.

1175
01:01:09,810 --> 01:01:11,810
I love you, Angela.

1176
01:01:13,840 --> 01:01:15,340
Whatever your fist name...

1177
01:01:15,870 --> 01:01:16,870
You're right.

1178
01:01:17,500 --> 01:01:18,500
Say it again...

1179
01:01:18,501 --> 01:01:20,300
... without my name.

1180
01:01:23,500 --> 01:01:25,500
I love you.

1181
01:01:26,880 --> 01:01:27,880
Good.

1182
01:01:29,020 --> 01:01:33,325
Now, look at yourself in the eye
and say it.

1183
01:01:45,930 --> 01:01:46,930
I can't.

1184
01:01:46,931 --> 01:01:47,931
Of course you can.

1185
01:01:49,260 --> 01:01:52,520
Look at your body.
Bruised by the lack of love...

1186
01:01:52,521 --> 01:01:53,521
... of trust.

1187
01:01:54,850 --> 01:01:57,860
Don't you see it deserves your attention?

1188
01:01:57,861 --> 01:02:00,850
So, don't reject this wounded body.

1189
01:02:00,851 --> 01:02:03,650
