1194
01:02:36,380 --> 01:02:39,992
I love you... Andre.

1195
01:02:41,580 --> 01:02:43,580
I love you.

1196
01:02:45,960 --> 01:02:48,000
I am proud of you, Andre.

1197
01:02:49,900 --> 01:02:52,650
So? Can we get some food?
I'm hungry...

1198
01:02:53,670 --> 01:02:55,080
You're obsessed with food, aren't you?

1199
01:02:55,081 --> 01:02:56,580
Do you have an emotional problem?

1200
01:02:56,581 --> 01:02:58,800
Hey, that's my line!

1201
01:02:59,350 --> 01:03:00,350
