1203
01:03:12,251 --> 01:03:13,750
We'll wash the dishes...

1204
01:03:14,070 --> 01:03:14,751
It only worked in the Dark Ages.

1205
01:03:15,650 --> 01:03:17,140
They're going to call the cops.
And we'll end up in jail.

1206
01:03:17,141 --> 01:03:18,980
I have a 6 months suspended sentence.
I know where I'm...

1207
01:03:18,981 --> 01:03:21,650
Stop complaining, now.
Just enjoy.

1208
01:03:21,651 --> 01:03:23,050
The wine is good, isn't it?

1209
01:03:23,051 --> 01:03:24,051
What kind is it?

1210
01:03:24,052 --> 01:03:25,052
Chateau Cheval Blanc.

1211
01:03:26,750 --> 01:03:27,750
Cheval Blanc?

1212
01:03:28,640 --> 01:03:29,510
It's 1,000 Euros!

1213
01:03:29,511 --> 01:03:31,840
1,500
It was the most expensive.

1214
01:03:31,841 --> 01:03:33,500
It sucks.
This place sucks.

1215
01:03:33,501 --> 01:03:35,100
Being the most expensive
doesn't mean it's the best, Angela.

1216
01:03:35,101 --> 01:03:37,050
How would you know?
You deal in olive oil.

1217
01:03:37,051 --> 01:03:39,200
Yes, but I know a thing or two.
I...

1218
01:03:39,201 --> 01:03:42,730
I'm sure the menu has some good little wines,
at very reasonable prices.

1219
01:03:42,731 --> 01:03:45,690
Look! Saint Chignon '98.
100 Euros. I'm sure it's good.

1220
01:03:45,691 --> 01:03:46,691
Sommelier!

1221
01:03:46,692 --> 01:03:47,675
Yes?

1222
01:03:47,676 --> 01:03:48,229
What are you doing?

1223
01:03:48,230 --> 01:03:50,000
Well... we're going to taste.

1224
01:03:50,300 --> 01:03:52,620
Can we have a Saint Chignon '98, please?

1225
01:03:52,621 --> 01:03:55,040
Oh, of course.
It's almost at maturity right now.

1226
01:03:55,041 --> 01:03:56,960
It's a bit peppery, a little round.

1227
01:03:56,970 --> 01:03:58,900
It's a very good wine.
A very good choice.

1228
01:03:58,901 --> 01:03:59,800
It's my favourite.

1229
01:03:59,801 --> 01:04:01,575
Can we simply have half a bottle?

1230
01:04:01,576 --> 01:04:03,945
No, we only have liters, here.

1231
01:04:05,940 --> 01:04:07,540
You're crazy!
I swear... you're totally crazy.

1232
01:04:07,541 --> 01:04:09,780
You've had a hard day.
I'm trying to please you.

1233
01:04:09,781 --> 01:04:11,370
Is that your mission?
Pleasing me?

1234
01:04:11,371 --> 01:04:15,030
No. I'm supposed to teach you
the most things as quickly as possible.

1235
01:04:15,031 --> 01:04:16,870
So that you give up jumping from bridges.

1236
01:04:16,871 --> 01:04:19,570
If you intend to pay the bill
by doing dirty things in the restroom...

1237
01:04:19,571 --> 01:04:21,260
... I won't wait for you at the bar.
I'm warning you.

1238
01:04:21,261 --> 01:04:22,400
What dirty stuff?

1239
01:04:22,401 --> 01:04:24,850
Don't act innocent... I was there,
behind the door. I've seen everything.

1240
01:04:26,425 --> 01:04:28,500
Have you seen...
or heard?

1241
01:04:32,500 --> 01:04:33,660
Angela?

1242
01:04:34,645 --> 01:04:35,645
What?

1243
01:04:36,250 --> 01:04:37,250
What're you doing?

1244
01:04:38,750 --> 01:04:39,750
Guess...

1245
01:04:40,800 --> 01:04:42,800
I don't want...
I don't want you do do this for me.

1246
01:04:42,801 --> 01:04:44,000
I thought you needed money.

1247
01:04:44,001 --> 01:04:46,240
Yes, I need it.
But I still have some morality left.

1248
01:04:46,241 --> 01:04:49,000
I thank you for it...
I appreciate the gesture...

1249
01:04:49,001 --> 01:04:50,700
But no, really.
No way you're doing this at all.

1250
01:04:50,701 --> 01:04:52,725
Come on...
It's nothing.

1251
01:04:52,726 --> 01:04:53,726
Yes, it's something!

1252
01:04:53,727 --> 01:04:55,710
Listen. Stop right now.
Ask this man to go back home.

