01:04:55,711 --> 01:04:56,750
Come out, right now!

1254
01:04:56,760 --> 01:04:59,050
Can't you give me a break,
so that I can finish? Fuck!

1255
01:05:03,445 --> 01:05:04,945
And what about Frank, then?

1256
01:05:04,946 --> 01:05:07,170
In his office...
What did you do?

1257
01:05:09,980 --> 01:05:10,980
You didn't do that!

1258
01:05:11,050 --> 01:05:12,930
No...
Just kidding.

1259
01:05:13,980 --> 01:05:14,980
What a relief...

1260
01:05:16,230 --> 01:05:18,050
But how did you get the money?

1261
01:05:29,000 --> 01:05:30,000
You can't have done that!

1262
01:05:30,001 --> 01:05:32,425
Which option would you rather have?

1263
01:05:33,645 --> 01:05:34,645
I'd rather go away.

1264
01:05:44,810 --> 01:05:45,700
For a single night, is that it?

1265
01:05:45,701 --> 01:05:46,320
Yes.

1266
01:05:46,321 --> 01:05:47,321
Good.

1267
01:05:48,900 --> 01:05:49,900
All done.

1268
01:05:50,500 --> 01:05:52,000
Do you have...
any luggage?

1269
01:05:52,001 --> 01:05:54,150
Yes. One item.
Right in front.

1270
01:06:07,720 --> 01:06:09,220
Feeling better?

1271
01:06:09,221 --> 01:06:10,700
Yeah, I'm fine...

1272
01:06:10,701 --> 01:06:11,990
Are you coming to bed?

1273
01:06:13,360 --> 01:06:14,150
No, I'm looking at the city.

1274
01:06:14,151 --> 01:06:16,400
It'll still be there tomorrow.
Come to bed.

1275
01:06:16,401 --> 01:06:18,100
Paris is beautiful.

1276
01:06:19,920 --> 01:06:21,150
I wasn't seeing anything.

1277
01:06:21,151 --> 01:06:23,780
I was blind like a bat.

1278
01:06:25,270 --> 01:06:26,270
Angela...

1279
01:06:26,271 --> 01:06:27,271
What?

1280
01:06:28,430 --> 01:06:29,650
I think I love you.

1281
01:06:29,900 --> 01:06:32,000
No you don't...
You're horny, that's all.

1282
01:06:32,001 --> 01:06:35,800
You're lacking affection.
So you're hanging on to the first one you run into.

1283
01:06:35,801 --> 01:06:37,000
i.e. : me!

1284
01:06:37,001 --> 01:06:39,800
No, no... Really.
You make me feel good.

1285
01:06:41,200 --> 01:06:42,750
I love how you shake me up.

1286
01:06:42,751 --> 01:06:45,000
Without ever judging me.

1287
01:06:45,001 --> 01:06:46,850
It makes me happy.

1288
01:06:48,620 --> 01:06:50,260
It's been a while since this happened to me.

1289
01:06:50,261 --> 01:06:51,750
It probably never did.

1290
01:06:52,050 --> 01:06:53,750
You want to fuck, that's all.

1291
01:06:53,751 --> 01:06:55,630
No, I don't want to fuck...

1292
01:06:56,650 --> 01:06:58,650
Actually, I do,
but that's not it.

1293
01:06:59,400 --> 01:07:00,900
It's stronger.
Warmer...

1294
01:07:00,901 --> 01:07:02,875
Oh la la!
You're waxing sentimental.

1295
01:07:02,876 --> 01:07:03,700
Come on, let's fuck!

1296
01:07:03,701 --> 01:07:05,625
No no no! Stop that!
What are you doing? Hey!

1297
01:07:06,640 --> 01:07:08,000
Don't you like me?

1298
01:07:09,350 --> 01:07:11,500
Yes, yes... I do.
But I don't want to fuck.

1299
01:07:11,501 --> 01:07:15,940
I'd like to make love.
But I'll only do it once I feel...

1300
01:07:16,500 --> 01:07:17,500
...free.

1301
01:07:18,050 --> 01:07:19,500
And what about me?

1302
01:07:21,350 --> 01:07:22,720
It won't take long.

1303
01:07:24,030 --> 01:07:26,430
Come on...
Come to bed.

1304
01:07:26,431 --> 01:07:27,431
I can't sleep.

1305
01:07:27,432 --> 01:07:29,500
And there's no point in brooding.

1306
01:07:29,501 --> 01:07:31,740
I'm not brooding.
I'm enjoying the room.

1307
01:07:32,430 --> 01:07:33,600
It's incredible.

1308
01:07:33,601 --> 01:07:35,475
By the way...
How are we going to pay for it?

1309
01:07:35,476 --> 01:07:37,850
I have an agreement with the head porter.

1310
01:07:37,851 --> 01:07:38,851
How so?

1311
01:07:38,852 --> 01:07:40,920
He bets on races.

1312
01:07:40,921 --> 01:07:42,640
So I gave him a tip.

1313
01:07:42,641 --> 01:07:43,641
A bad tip?

1314
01:07:43,642 --> 01:07:45,450
No, he's going to make 10,000 Euros.

1315
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:47,200
You know races results?

1316
01:07:47,201 --> 01:07:48,640
Any race.
Anywhere in the world.

1317
01:07:48,641 --> 01:07:51,160
Are you kidding me?
You let me bet on that rotten Brutus...

1318
01:07:51,161 --> 01:07:52,161
I had warned you.

1319
01:07:52,162 --> 01:07:54,785
But a few hours ago
you wouldn't listen to me.

1320
01:07:54,786 --> 01:07:58,500
And anyway... I'm not allowed to
give away that kind of information.

1321
01:07:58,501 --> 01:07:59,501
It's forbidden.

1322
01:08:00,300 --> 01:08:02,000
You're not allowed to
give away that kind of information?

1323
01:08:02,001 --> 01:08:04,450
Why... Why did you tell me
that you're an angel, then?

1324
01:08:07,450 --> 01:08:08,950
I shouldn't have.

1325
01:08:10,025 --> 01:08:11,350
Why did you do it, then?

1326
01:08:19,640 --> 01:08:20,640
Hey!

1327
01:08:21,310 --> 01:08:22,325
What are you doing, Angela?

1328
01:08:22,326 --> 01:08:24,180
I'm off to see your buddy Frank.

1329
01:08:24,181 --> 01:08:26,125
What? In the middle of the night?
What are you going to tell him?

1330
01:08:26,126 --> 01:08:28,200
I'm not the one who has things to tell him.
You are!

1331
01:08:28,201 --> 01:08:31,275
So we're going to see him.
And you'll tell him everything you need.

1332
01:08:31,276 --> 01:08:33,260
So that I can go back home.

1333
01:08:33,900 --> 01:08:34,900
Angela...

1334
01:08:37,240 --> 01:08:39,150
Okay...
So, what should I tell him?

1335
01:08:39,940 --> 01:08:41,000
You're doing it again...

1336
01:08:41,001 --> 01:08:42,300
I told you a hundred times!

1337
01:08:42,301 --> 01:08:43,900
The truth!
Nothing but the truth.

1338
01:08:43,901 --> 01:08:45,500
The truth.
No problem. Okay.

1339
01:08:45,640 --> 01:08:48,450
If you don't do that, your pain
will stay here, in a ball.

1340
01:08:48,451 --> 01:08:50,400
It's weaker, but it's still here, yeah...

1341
01:08:50,401 --> 01:08:53,110
You've got to get it out.
Once for all!

1342
01:08:53,111 --> 01:08:55,300
If it's outside,
it won't trouble you inside anymore.

1343
01:08:55,301 --> 01:08:56,920
Okay. No problem.
I agree.

1344
01:08:56,921 --> 01:08:57,921
And after that?

1345
01:08:57,922 --> 01:09:01,580
After that? You'll be cleared, on the inside.
You'll just have to fill up.

1346
01:09:02,410 --> 01:09:04,185
Angela...
What if it's with you that I want to fill up?

1347
01:09:04,186 --> 01:09:05,750
Ah...
Don't do that again.

1348
01:09:05,751 --> 01:09:08,050
Angela, I'm in love with you.

1349
01:09:08,051 --> 01:09:10,010
You see everything.
You feel everything...

1350
01:09:10,900 --> 01:09:13,350
How can't you see
something this simple?

1351
01:09:14,310 --> 01:09:16,660
Focus, please.
Right here...

1352
01:09:18,000 --> 01:09:19,580
What do you feel?

1353
01:09:22,050 --> 01:09:23,000
I feel something, but...

1354
01:09:23,001 --> 01:09:25,950
I feel exactly the same thing.

1355
01:09:26,900 --> 01:09:28,600
And now I know how it's called.

1356
01:09:30,080 --> 01:09:31,080
Anyway...

1357
01:09:31,081 --> 01:09:32,081
Let's go meet Frank...

1358
01:09:32,082 --> 01:09:35,100
Things are getting really messy.

1359
01:09:36,690 --> 01:09:39,900
No.
Things only start to looking clear now.

1360
01:09:40,490 --> 01:09:41,490
Like...

1361
01:09:42,100 --> 01:09:43,650
Looking like the truth, for instance.

1362
01:09:45,945 --> 01:09:47,815
I'm tired, Angela... I swear.

1363
01:09:49,670 --> 01:09:51,810
I'm tired of screwing up all the time.

1364
01:09:51,811 --> 01:09:53,750
Tired of lies...

1365
01:09:57,400 --> 01:09:59,690
For the first time in my life,
I want to be true.

1366
01:10:03,235 --> 01:10:05,400
I'll be able to say everything I feel.

1367
01:10:05,401 --> 01:10:06,401
Everything.

1368
01:10:10,000 --> 01:10:11,160
Do you know what I'm feeling, Angela?

1369
01:10:11,650 --> 01:10:12,650
Shut up.

1370
01:10:19,850 --> 01:10:21,650
Miss!
Miss!

1371
01:10:21,651 --> 01:10:23,350
Miss, please...
Miss.

1372
01:10:24,950 --> 01:10:27,800
Now is really not the time to fuck with me.

1373
01:10:30,180 --> 01:10:32,980
Sorry for interrupting you like that
in the middle of the night...

1374
01:10:32,981 --> 01:10:34,900
... but Andre has something
very important to tell you.

1375
01:10:34,901 --> 01:10:37,160
I can't take it anymore,
and I want to go home...

1376
01:10:37,161 --> 01:10:38,800
...so let's end this now!

1377
01:10:38,801 --> 01:10:39,600
Come again?

1378
01:10:39,670 --> 01:10:40,320
Who's that girl?

1379
01:10:40,321 --> 01:10:42,100
You!
Shut the hell up!

1380
01:10:42,101 --> 01:10:43,200
Andre! Come in!

1381
01:10:43,201 --> 01:10:45,600
He's here.
In his bed...

1382
01:10:45,601 --> 01:10:47,210
What the fuck is this?

1383
01:10:50,600 --> 01:10:52,620
When you start breaking the rules,
you really go for it...

1384
01:10:52,621 --> 01:10:54,615
The door...
The bodyguard...

1385
01:10:55,720 --> 01:10:57,950
And you chose this place because you knew
that's where he would stay.

1386
01:10:57,951 --> 01:10:59,550
You're going to be fired.

1387
01:10:59,551 --> 01:11:01,550
That's not your business.
It's mine.

1388
01:11:01,551 --> 01:11:04,000
Be nice, now.
And deal with him quickly...

1389
01:11:04,001 --> 01:11:05,150
... so that we can get the hell away.

1390
01:11:06,820 --> 01:11:07,820
Okay.

1391
01:11:10,250 --> 01:11:11,250
Andre...

1392
01:11:12,280 --> 01:11:13,280
Andre...

1393
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:20,030
You're not going to kill me, aren't you?

1394
01:11:26,260 --> 01:11:28,300
Your coffee isn't bad, Frank.

1395
01:11:31,190 --> 01:11:34,700
Andre... I... I... I...
I'm sorry.

1396
01:11:34,701 --> 01:11:36,100
I... I know I offended you.

1397
01:11:36,101 --> 01:11:37,500
And it really was stupid of me, buddy.

1398
01:11:37,800 --> 01:11:38,400
Buddy?

1399
01:11:38,700 --> 01:11:39,900
No. Sorry about that.

1400
01:11:40,850 --> 01:11:43,500
I took advantage of your weakness, sir,
and really I shouldn't have.

1401
01:11:43,501 --> 01:11:45,100
That... that was pathetic of me.

1402
01:11:46,240 --> 01:11:49,400
There's even some business we could do together.
If you want... That is, if you have the time

1403
01:11:49,401 --> 01:11:53,473
But I beg you... Andy.

1404
01:11:54,700 --> 01:11:58,130
Do not kill me.
Be nice... do not kill me.

1405
01:11:59,050 --> 01:12:01,005
I'm sorry I borrowed money from you, Frank.

1406
01:12:01,006 --> 01:12:03,050
It's my fault.
I'm the one to blame.

1407
01:12:03,850 --> 01:12:05,930
In the first place, I should never have
set foot in your lousy club.

1408
01:12:05,931 --> 01:12:07,000
It cost me time and money...

1409
01:12:07,001 --> 01:12:09,550
Instead of taking care of the business
for which I came to Paris.

1410
01:12:10,250 --> 01:12:11,600
But there's no escaping it.

1411
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:15,370
When you feel like shit, you're attracted by
the other pieces of shit like you. That's life.

1412
01:12:16,450 --> 01:12:18,700
That's why we used to get along fine,
in the beginning, Frank.

1413
01:12:18,701 --> 01:12:22,100
We could hate each other mutually.
That wasn't a problem.

1414
01:12:26,700 --> 01:12:29,000
One day, an angel entered my life.

1415
01:12:30,450 --> 01:12:32,610
A wonderful woman, who opened my eyes.

1416
01:12:34,880 --> 01:12:37,250
It's so good to have the eyes opened, Frank.

1417
01:12:39,600 --> 01:12:42,000
Now I can look at the sun, rising over Paris.

1418
01:12:42,001 --> 01:12:45,250
All these small lightbulbs...
switching off, one by one.

1419
01:12:46,100 --> 01:12:47,900
I can see all this, Frank.

1420
01:12:50,100 --> 01:12:51,500
And it's thanks to her.

1421
01:12:52,550 --> 01:12:55,100
Because she had the kindness never to judge me.

1422
01:12:58,900 --> 01:13:00,500
She loved me as I was.

1423
01:13:02,300 --> 01:13:04,900
Even though I wasn't much.

1424
01:13:09,500 --> 01:13:11,600
I am happy for you, Andre.
Sincerely.

1425
01:13:11,601 --> 01:13:14,401
But you're not going to kill me, aren't you?

1426
01:13:15,350 --> 01:13:16,350
No.

1427
01:13:17,600 --> 01:13:19,300
I'm going to feel sorry for you.

1428
01:13:20,550 --> 01:13:23,000
Did you see that, Angela?
I did really good, for a first time!

1429
01:13:23,001 --> 01:13:24,001
Where are you?

1430
01:13:24,002 --> 01:13:25,002
Angela?

1431
01:13:28,500 --> 01:13:29,500
Angela...

1432
01:14:23,130 --> 01:14:24,250
Angela, what are you doing?
Where are you going?

1433
01:14:24,251 --> 01:14:25,050
I'm going home.

1434
01:14:25,051 --> 01:14:26,590
You can't do this to me.
It's impossible.

1435
01:14:26,591 --> 01:14:28,800
Angela, stop!
I did all you asked me to do.

1436
01:14:28,801 --> 01:14:30,540
Look!
I've emptied everything.

1437
01:14:30,541 --> 01:14:32,400
Now we can start over, together.

1438
01:14:32,401 --> 01:14:34,715
We'll be together, choosing the things
that will fullfill me. Like we said.

1439
01:14:34,716 --> 01:14:36,300
You're big enough to choose on your own, now.

1440
01:14:36,301 --> 01:14:37,650
I don't want to choose on my own!

1441
01:14:37,651 --> 01:14:39,380
I want to do this with you, Angela.

1442
01:14:39,381 --> 01:14:41,980
Because I love you. And I want to spend
the time I have left to live at your side.

1443
01:14:41,981 --> 01:14:44,535
If you leave me, it's going to be horrible.
I'll be falling back on my old habits.

1444
01:14:44,536 --> 01:14:46,090
As if I had gone this far for nothing.

1445
01:14:46,091 --> 01:14:48,540
Well... too bad.
Destroy yourself if you want.

1446
01:14:48,541 --> 01:14:50,250
I took many chances for you.

1447
01:14:50,251 --> 01:14:52,465
I've got a 9/10 chance of being fired.

1448
01:14:52,466 --> 01:14:54,700
So please be helpful, Andre.
Don't ruin it all.

1449
01:14:54,701 --> 01:14:56,250
And live the life you are meant to live.

1450
01:14:57,750 --> 01:14:59,735
Angela! What if the life I'm meant to live was
the one where I'm staying with you?

1451
01:14:59,736 --> 01:15:02,900
No! I already know your life entirely.

1452
01:15:02,901 --> 01:15:05,050
In two months, you will create your company.

1453
01:15:05,051 --> 01:15:08,700
In five years, it's going to be the leading olive oil business.

1454
01:15:09,200 --> 01:15:12,000
You're going to meet Catherine.
A lovely 30 years old lawyer.

1455
01:15:12,001 --> 01:15:14,850
With whom you will have three beautiful children.

1456
01:15:14,851 --> 01:15:16,870
Do you want to know their names?

1457
01:15:17,800 --> 01:15:20,550
Do you want to know how they'll do in school?

1458
01:15:22,920 --> 01:15:24,570
I want to know why you're crying.

1459
01:15:24,840 --> 01:15:27,465
Because...
Because it's always like that when a mission is completed.

1460
01:15:27,466 --> 01:15:29,580
I'm made for meeting.
Not for goodbyes.

1461
01:15:29,581 --> 01:15:31,660
Are you satisfied with this answer?

1462
01:15:32,975 --> 01:15:34,330
Listen to me.

1463
01:15:34,331 --> 01:15:36,190
What you've done for me was enormous.

1464
01:15:36,650 --> 01:15:37,600
You have my eternal appreciation.

1465
01:15:37,601 --> 01:15:40,550
'Eternal' ?
Please, don't use words you don't understand.

1466
01:15:40,551 --> 01:15:42,290
Angela, listen to me...
I'm sorry.

1467
01:15:43,000 --> 01:15:44,000
Forgive me.

1468
01:15:44,480 --> 01:15:47,840
You've taught me what matters :
to stop lying.

1469
01:15:50,380 --> 01:15:52,000
That's right.
That's the most important thing.

1470
01:15:52,001 --> 01:15:54,000
So why don't you stop lying yourself!

1471
01:15:56,450 --> 01:15:58,050
Angela, stop!
Listen to me.

1472
01:15:58,051 --> 01:15:59,715
Look at me.
Look at me in the eye.

1473
01:15:59,716 --> 01:16:00,235
Stop!

1474
01:16:00,236 --> 01:16:01,236
Look at me.

1475
01:16:02,550 --> 01:16:03,700
Leave me alone.

1476
01:16:03,701 --> 01:16:05,300
Let me tell you what I see in these eyes...

1477
01:16:05,500 --> 01:16:09,270
I see a woman who doesn't want to leave.
A woman who's tired of not knowing who she is.

1478
01:16:10,580 --> 01:16:13,466
Like me, nobody ever told you he loved you.
And if someone did, you don't remember.

1479
01:16:13,467 --> 01:16:14,000
Shut up.

1480
01:16:14,100 --> 01:16:15,001
I love you, Angela!

1481
01:16:15,390 --> 01:16:15,940
Shut up.

1482
01:16:15,941 --> 01:16:17,400
I love you.

1483
01:16:18,375 --> 01:16:19,000
Shut up!

1484
01:16:19,080 --> 01:16:20,385
I can't live without you.
It's impossible!

1485
01:16:20,386 --> 01:16:22,650
What's the point of living with me?

1486
01:16:22,651 --> 01:16:24,150
What are you talking about?

1487
01:16:24,151 --> 01:16:26,120
I'd be an angel who burned her wings.

1488
01:16:26,121 --> 01:16:27,280
A fallen angel.

1489
01:16:27,281 --> 01:16:28,770
I don't care about that!

1490
01:16:28,771 --> 01:16:30,890
I love you the way you are.

1491
01:16:39,260 --> 01:16:40,500
I don't know...

1492
01:16:40,501 --> 01:16:42,250
...who I am!

1493
01:16:42,251 --> 01:16:44,100
I have no past.

1494
01:16:44,101 --> 01:16:45,400
Can you understand that?

1495
01:16:45,500 --> 01:16:46,150
I know... I know...

1496
01:16:46,151 --> 01:16:50,100
How can...
How can, I achieve anything?

1497
01:16:50,121 --> 01:16:51,121
I know...

1498
01:16:51,122 --> 01:16:53,335
... if I don't know where I come from.

1499
01:16:53,500 --> 01:16:58,260
I don't know where I come from.
I don't know where I come from...

1500
01:17:03,320 --> 01:17:05,630
I know...
I know.

1501
01:17:10,510 --> 01:17:12,500
